{"tid":2326904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔夠兩個星期就到聖誕","createTime":"2020-12-15T15:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T16:32:00.000Z","uid":370062,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2a8d4ca00b270a0704bb92e0bf1c331e99edd6","tid":2326904,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:56:01.000Z","msg":"希望各位連登巴絲可以開開心心過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論親情友情定愛情都可以一直保持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕當日約咗屋企人朋友另一半嘅玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未約嘅希望你哋快啲約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溝緊仔或女嘅希望你哋快啲溝到然後甜甜蜜蜜過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之希望大家今年過個開心愉快幸福嘅聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好好似本行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f167ea5de0b74d3d577d1d781d9747ee348e20","tid":2326904,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db4aa4c25fd278e999c62e136e42e3f6ff5a1d0","tid":2326904,"uid":367090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"我理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e0f43ecff431a5fc1f968e57643dca115948c5","tid":2326904,"uid":302414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬 聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b90aa61fa0